# shadcn/ui — Prefer Over Default React/HTML

**Always use shadcn components** from this project’s UI registry (`@shadcn`) instead of default React or plain HTML elements when a matching shadcn component exists.

## Add before use

If a component is not yet in the project, add it with:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

Use the project’s configured registry (e.g. `@shadcn`). Check `components.json` for the registry.

## Mapping: default → shadcn

| Need | Don’t use | Use shadcn |
|------|-----------|------------|
| Button | `<button>`, custom btn | `Button` |
| Links that look like buttons | `<a>` + custom styles | `Button` with `asChild` + `Link` |
| Form inputs | `<input>` | `Input` (or `InputGroup`, `InputOTP` if applicable) |
| Text area | `<textarea>` | `Textarea` |
| Checkbox | `<input type="checkbox">` | `Checkbox` |
| Radio group | `<input type="radio">` | `RadioGroup` |
| Toggle on/off | custom div | `Switch` |
| Dropdown / menu | custom div + state | `DropdownMenu` |
| Modal / dialog | custom modal | `Dialog` or `AlertDialog` |
| Sheet (drawer) | custom drawer | `Sheet` or `Drawer` |
| Popover | custom positioned div | `Popover` |
| Tooltip | custom title/div | `Tooltip` |
| Select (single) | `<select>` | `Select` (or `NativeSelect` when appropriate) |
| Tabs | custom state + divs | `Tabs` |
| Cards | plain divs | `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardContent`, `CardFooter` |
| Badge / tag | `<span>` styled | `Badge` |
| Avatar | `<img>` rounded | `Avatar` |
| Loading spinner | custom spinner | `Spinner` |
| Progress bar | custom div | `Progress` |
| Skeleton loaders | custom placeholders | `Skeleton` |
| Tables | raw `<table>` | `Table`, `TableHeader`, `TableBody`, `TableRow`, `TableCell` |
| Breadcrumbs | manual links | `Breadcrumb` |
| Pagination | custom buttons | `Pagination` |
| Labels | `<label>` only | `Label` (from shadcn) |
| Forms (with validation) | raw form | `Form` + react-hook-form + zod |
| Separator | `<hr>` or div | `Separator` |
| Scrollable area | overflow div | `ScrollArea` |
| Accordion / collapse | custom state | `Accordion` or `Collapsible` |
| Command palette / combobox | custom input + list | `Command` or `Combobox` |
| Calendar / date picker | raw input | `Calendar` (+ popover if needed) |
| Toasts / notifications | custom toast | `Sonner` or project toast pattern |

